# Terminal Use

[![PyPI version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/terminaluse.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/terminaluse/)

Deploy file system agents with Terminal Use. Manage deployed agents, and improve your agents systematically.

## Installation

```sh
pip install terminaluse
```

## CLI

```sh
tu --help
```

